net.sf.gogui.gogui
Class GoGuiSettings

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.gogui.gogui.GoGuiSettings

public final class GoGuiSettings
extends java.lang.Object

Parse command line options. Also modifies the persistent preferences if some command line options are set (e.g. komi) and handles some simple options that don't require the graphical startup of GoGui (e.g. -help).
